<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q19_v8" title="Q19_v8" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Se desea escribir la expresión
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          <m:mo>·</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mn>11</m:mn>
          </m:msqrt>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      en forma simplificada. ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones es equivalente a
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          <m:mo>·</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mn>11</m:mn>
          </m:msqrt>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      ?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>99</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión original es 4 · 3√11 = 12√11. En cambio, 4√99 = 4√(9·11) = 4·3√11 = 12√11, por lo que esta opción no está en forma simplificada, porque √99 todavía se puede simplificar a 3√11.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>12</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>11</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Se multiplican los factores que están fuera de la raíz: 4 · 3√11 = (4·3)√11 = 12√11. Además, 11 no tiene factores cuadrados perfectos distintos de 1, así que la expresión ya está simplificada.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>7</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>11</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión original es 4 · 3√11 = (4·3)√11 = 12√11, no 7√11. Como 12 ≠ 7, esta opción no es equivalente a la expresión dada.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>12</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>33</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión original es 4 · 3√11 = 12√11. Esta opción es 12√33. Como √33 ≠ √11, entonces 12√33 ≠ 12√11, por lo que no es equivalente a la expresión inicial.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la expresión dada</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>11</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Multiplicar los factores que están fuera de la raíz</strong></p>
            <p>Los números 4 y 3 están multiplicando a <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>11</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math>, así que:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>11</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>11</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Efectuar la multiplicación</strong></p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>11</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>12</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>11</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar si la raíz se puede simplificar</strong></p>
            <p>El número 11 no tiene factores cuadrados perfectos distintos de 1, por lo tanto <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mn>11</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:math> ya está simplificada.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión equivalente en forma simplificada es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>12</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>11</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>